se who are always whining about the complexity of games).</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The developer is not responsible for the nerves spent (reminder, there are no difficulty levels in the game, the game itself is hardcore and will continue to develop in this direction).</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The developer is not responsible for the broken psyche, and the standard idea of platformers <strong>with plush unicorns.</strong></p></li></ul>",
